      ** Other parms
      ** Field(s) requiring validation
      ** Yearly Cashflows Required
     C                   PARM                    DDS8VR
      ** Outputs
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
